  "title": "分数比较大小·作差法",
  "grade": "五年级",
  "module": "calc",
  "topic": "比较大小",
  "question": "比较 2023/2024 和 2024/2025 的大小。",
  "figures": [
    {
      "svg": "<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 450 120'><text x='20' y='40' font-size='22' font-family='monospace' fill='#333'>2023/2024  ○  2024/2025</text><text x='20' y='70' font-size='14' fill='#888'>两个分数都很接近 1，但哪个更大？</text><text x='20' y='95' font-size='14' fill='#E74C3C'>提示：用 1 减去每个分数，比较差值</text></svg>",
      "caption": "比较大小：用“1 − 分数”的方法（作差法）",
      "alt": "分数比较大小"
    }
  ],
  "solutions": [
    {
      "key": "difference",
      "label": "作差法（与1比较）",
      "steps": [
        "两个分数都小于 1 且非常接近 1，考虑用 1 减去每个分数。",
        "1 − 2023/2024 = 1/2024。",
        "1 − 2024/2025 = 1/2025。",
        "比较差值：1/2024 > 1/2025（分子相同，分母越小分数越大）。",
        "被减数相同（都是1），减去的差值越大，原分数越小。",
        "因此 2023/2024 < 2024/2025。"
      ],
      "scenes": [
        {
          "kind": "compare-bars",
          "rows": [
            {
              "label": "2023/2024",
              "value": "0.9995",
              "max": 1,
              "tone": "primary"
            },
            {
              "label": "2024/2025",
              "value": "0.9995",
              "max": 1,
              "tone": "muted"
            }
          ],
          "caption": "两个分数都非常接近 1"
        },
        {
          "kind": "equation-list",
          "rows": [
            { "lhs": "1 − 2023/2024", "rhs": "1/2024", "status": "keep" },
            { "lhs": "1 − 2024/2025", "rhs": "1/2025", "status": "keep" }
          ],
          "caption": "步骤1：计算与 1 的差距"
        },
        {
          "kind": "number-line",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "points": [
            { "value": 0.9995, "label": "2023/2024", "tone": "primary" },
            { "value": 0.9995, "label": "2024/2025", "tone": "accent" },
            { "value": 1, "label": "1", "tone": "default" }
          ],
          "segments": [
            { "from": 0.9995, "to": 1, "label": "1/2024", "tone": "primary" },
            {
              "from": 0.9995,
              "to": 1,
              "label": "1/2025 (更小)",
              "tone": "accent"
            }
          ],
          "caption": "步骤2：1/2024 > 1/2025，所以 2023/2024 离 1 更远"
        },
        {
          "kind": "result-badges",
          "items": [
            { "icon": "🔹", "count": "2023/2024", "label": "< 2024/2025" }
          ],
          "caption": "结论：2023/2024 < 2024/2025"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "reciprocal",
      "label": "倒数法",
      "steps": [
        "比较倒数：2023/2024 的倒数是 2024/2023 = 1 + 1/2023。",
        "2024/2025 的倒数是 2025/2024 = 1 + 1/2024。",
        "因为 1/2023 > 1/2024，所以倒数 2024/2023 > 2025/2024。",
        "倒数越大，原分数越小。因此 2023/2024 < 2024/2025。"
      ]
    }
  ],
